          [| inp(C) = inp(A); out(C)=out(A);
             is_fair_ref_map f C A |]
          ==> fair_implements C A"
apply (simp add: is_fair_ref_map_def fair_implements_def fairtraces_def fairexecutions_def)
apply auto
apply (rule_tac x = "corresp_ex A f ex" in exI)
